%20the%20finite%20supply%20of%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20get%20an%20AI%20model%20to%20use%20extra%20inference-time%20compute%20and%20improve%20its%20outputs%2C%20that's%20a%20way%20for%20it%20to%20generate%20better%20synthetic%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20useful%20new%20source%20of%20training%20data.%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20promising%20way%20to%20get%20around%20these%20pre-training%20data%20bottlenecks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233217231-9371-4a57-b7f5-b952a4f12038%5C%22%3ESatya%20satisfied%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20video%20podcast%2C%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20seemed%20unperturbed%20and%20even%20buoyant%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20slowdown%20in%20AI%20model%20improvement%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20new%20quality%20training%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20inference-time%20compute%20as%20%26quot%3Banother%20scaling%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20have%20pre-training%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20effectively%20this%20test-time%20sampling%20that%20then%20creates%20the%20tokens%20that%20can%20go%20back%20into%20pre-training%2C%20creating%20even%20more%20powerful%20models%20that%20then%20are%20running%20on%20your%20inference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20I%20think%20a%20fantastic%20way%20to%20increase%20model%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20added%2C%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESutskever%20also%20mentioned%20test-time%20compute%20as%20one%20possible%20solution%20to%20the%20peak-data%20problem%2C%20during%20his%20Neurips%20talk%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276abeae5-ec9e-4c2d-aad9-de6615d1309f%5C%22%3ETest%20time%20for%20test-time%20compute%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E2025%20will%20see%20this%20approach%20put%20to%20the%20test.%20It's%20not%20a%20slam-dunk%2C%20although%20Snell%20is%20optimistic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20three%20years%20or%20so%2C%20it%20seemed%20more%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20AI%20progress.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20in%20this%20exploratory%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20open%20question%3A%20How%20well%20does%20this%20test-time%20compute%20technique%20generalize%3F%20Snell%20said%20it%20performs%20well%20with%20questions%20where%20the%20answer%20is%20knowable%20and%20you%20can%20check%20it%2C%20such%20as%20a%20math%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20need%20reasoning%20aren't%20easy%20to%20check.%20For%20instance%2C%20writing%20an%20essay.%20There's%20often%20no%20straight%20answer%20on%20how%20good%20this%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20are%20early%20signs%20of%20success%20and%20Snell%20suspects%20outputs%20from%20these%20types%20of%20reasoning%20AI%20models%20are%20already%20being%20used%20to%20train%20new%20models.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20this%20synthetic%20data%20is%20better%20than%20what's%20out%20on%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20outputs%20from%20OpenAI's%20o1%20model%20are%20better%20than%20GPT-4%2C%20the%20startup's%20previous%20top%20model%2C%20then%20these%20new%20outputs%20can%20in%20theory%20be%20reused%20for%20future%20AI%20model%20training%2C%20Snell%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20a%20theoretical%20example%3A%20Say%20o1%20gets%20a%2090%25%20score%20on%20a%20particular%20AI%20benchmark%2C%20you%20could%20take%20those%20answers%20and%20feed%20them%20to%20GPT-4%20and%20get%20that%20model%20up%20to%2090%25%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20large%20set%20of%20prompts%2C%20you%20could%20get%20a%20bunch%20of%20data%20from%20o1%20and%20create%20a%20large%20set%20of%20training%20examples%20and%20pre-train%20a%20new%20model%20on%20them%2C%20or%20continue%20training%20GPT-4%20to%20be%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Snell%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20TechCrunch%20report%20from%20late%20December%20suggested%20that%20DeepSeek%20may%20have%20used%20outputs%20from%20OpenAI's%20o1%20to%20train%20its%20own%20AI%20model.%20Its%20latest%20offering%2C%20called%20DeepSeek%20V3%2C%20performs%20well%20on%20industry%20benchmarks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20probably%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20reproduce%20o1%2C%26quot%3B%20Snell%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20asked%20people%20at%20OpenAI%20what%20they%20think%20of%20it.%20They%20say%20it%20looks%20like%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20how%20DeepSeek%20did%20this%20so%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20DeepSeek%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-peak-data-google-deepmind-researchers-solution-test-time-compute-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736071861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67771f77e5726ab18d0e5d2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-peak-data-google-deepmind-researchers-solution-test-time-compute-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20not%20enough%20human-generated%20data%20to%20keep%20AI%20models%20improving%20at%20the%20same%20rate.%202025%20will%20put%20a%20new%20solution%20to%20the%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-peak-data-google-deepmind-researchers-solution-test-time-compute-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'AAP-da%20govt%20doesn't%20have%20vision%20to%20develop%20Delhi'%2C%20says%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736071673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com