%20premiums%2C%20and%20property%20taxes%20while%20also%20facing%20a%20scarcity%20of%20affordable%20retirement%20housing%20options.%20And%20working%20all%20their%20lives%20isn't%20enough%20to%20prevent%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20older%20people%20from%20experiencing%20homelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERising%20rents%20and%20home%20prices%2C%20largely%20caused%20by%20a%20housing%20shortage%20and%20other%20cost-of-living%20spikes%2C%20are%20hitting%20older%20adults%20especially%20hard.%20Overall%20homelessness%20surged%20to%20its%20highest%20level%20on%20record%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hud.gov%2Fpress%2Fpress_releases_media_advisories%2FHUD_No_24_327%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20government's%20most%20recent%20count%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20January%202024.%20And%20older%20people%20make%20up%20a%20growing%20share%20of%20those%20losing%20their%20homes%3A%20The%20portion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governing.com%2Furban%2Fthe-nations-homeless-population-is-aging-dramatically%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeless%20single%20adults%2050%20or%20older%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20grown%20from%20about%2010%25%20to%2050%25%20over%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20housing%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20everything%2C%20quite%20frankly%2C%20is%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Marcy%20Thompson%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20programs%20and%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20Alliance%20to%20End%20Homelessness%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20particularly%20true%20for%20older%20adults%20who%20are%20on%20fixed%20incomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22893b1d7c-ea3d-4126-8480-fc8516964e40%5C%22%3EHomeowners%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20homelessness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EValerie%20Miller%2C%2067%2C%20has%20owned%20her%20mobile%20home%20in%20San%20Bernardino%2C%20California%20for%20almost%2035%20years%2C%20but%20she's%20still%20struggling%20to%20pay%20rent%20for%20the%20plot%20her%20home%20sits%20on%20and%20can't%20afford%20needed%20repairs%20and%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%2C%20who%20never%20married%20or%20had%20children%2C%20is%20planning%20to%20wait%20until%20she's%2070%20to%20collect%20Social%20Security%20but%20has%20already%20begun%20dipping%20into%20her%20meager%20retirement%20savings%20and%20worries%20she'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20leave%20her%20job%20at%20a%20truck-permitting%20company.%20Miller%20has%20considered%20selling%20her%20home%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20know%20where%20she%20could%20find%20more%20affordable%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20lie%20awake%20at%20night%20and%20I'm%20so%20worried%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20up%20all%20my%20savings%2C%20and%20then%20what%20do%20I%20do%3F%20Live%20off%20credit%20cards%20or%20go%20with%20the%20homeless%20people%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20homelessness%20among%20older%20Americans%20is%20a%20result%20both%20of%20demographic%20shifts%20%E2%80%94%20the%20baby%20boomer%20generation%20is%20getting%20older%20%E2%80%94%20and%20rising%20housing%20and%20other%20costs.%20The%20number%20of%20older%20homeowners%20and%20renters%20who%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jchs.harvard.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Freports%2Ffiles%2FHarvard_JCHS_The_State_of_the_Nations_Housing_2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2030%25%20of%20their%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20housing%20costs%20has%20surged%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllison%20Nickerson%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20LiveOn%20NY%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20group%20focused%20on%20improving%20living%20conditions%20for%20aging%20people%2C%20argued%20that%20Americans%20tend%20to%20underestimate%20the%20number%20of%20older%20people%20suffering.%20A%20fifth%20of%20Americans%2050%20and%20older%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-baby-boomers-savings-cant-afford-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20retirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20feeling%20that%20baby%20boomers%20and%20older%20people%20are%20pretty%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20you%20actually%20look%20at%20the%20the%20amount%20of%20people%20who%20are%20struggling%2C%20and%20then%20looking%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20that%20has%20gone%20up%2C%20inflation%20that's%20gone%20up%2C%20people%20are%20just%20getting%20left%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarbara%20Willing%2C%2069%2C%20an%20artist%20who's%20worked%20on%20and%20off%20at%20Walmart%20and%20Lowe's%2C%20has%20struggled%20to%20make%20a%20steady%20income%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20she%20suffers%20from%20an%20autoimmune%20disease.%20She%20bought%20her%20home%20in%20Victor%2C%20Montana%20%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20town%2035%20miles%20south%20of%20Missoula%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20twenty%20years%20ago%20and%20is%20still%20paying%20off%20her%20mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20place%20I'm%20in%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20inadequate%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20because%20to%20move%20would%20cost%20me%20so%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Willing%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20her%20home%20has%20electrical%20and%20plumbing%20issues.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20fear%20of%20losing%20her%20home%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20loom%20and%20gnaw%20on%20my%20conscience%20and%20nerves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilling%20has%20been%20out%20of%20work%20since%20July%20and%20is%20looking%20for%20her%20next%20sales%20job%2C%20but%20she%20worries%20her%20aging%20car%20won't%20last%20long%20traveling%20the%20nearly%20two-hour%20roundtrip%20commute%20to%20Missoula%20should%20she%20find%20a%20job%20there.%20Without%20any%20retirement%20savings%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20relying%20largely%20on%20her%20small%20Social%20Security%20check