%2580%2593%2520Sometimes%252C%2520zero%2520drinks%2520is%2Con%2520your%2520body%2520and%2520mind.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Coast%20Guard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%201-2-3%20rule%20is%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENo%20more%20than%20one%20standard%20drink%20per%20hour%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENo%20more%20than%20two%20standard%20drinks%20per%20occasion%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENo%20more%20than%20three%20drinks%20a%20day%20(more%20than%20three%20constitutes%20binge%20drinking%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niaaa.nih.gov%2Falcohols-effects-health%2Falcohol-drinking-patterns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20on%20Alcohol%20Abuse%20and%20Alcoholism%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMetzelaar%20says%20there%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20answer%26quot%3B%20to%20alcohol%20consumption%2C%20but%20the%201-2-3%20rule%20roughly%20falls%20in%20line%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Falcohol%2Fabout-alcohol-use%2Fmoderate-alcohol-use.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECDC's%20advisory%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20no%20more%20than%20a%20drink%20a%20day%20for%20women%20and%20two%20drinks%20a%20day%20for%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you%20about%20your%20drinking%20habits.%20If%20you're%20comfortable%20sharing%20with%20a%20reporter%2C%20please%20fill%20out%20this%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScB-4a6dV6jak2g6t-CoOdxFIENDSZggxHVbvsz6ry4dGoUjg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Note%3A%20We%20won't%20publish%20any%20part%20of%20your%20submission%20unless%20we%20contact%20you%20first.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20not%20a%20perfect%20rule%2C%2