C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20pressure%20to%20be%20a%20perfect%20parent%20now%20extends%20to%20childbirth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pregnant%20woman%20surrounded%20by%20social%20media%20images%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67743121ca1058716a5ee294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Pedro%20Nekoi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20after%20a%20long%20day%20of%20work%20and%20several%20wrestling%20matches%20with%20my%2030-pound%20toddler%2C%20I%20collapsed%20onto%20my%20couch%20and%20opened%20my%20phone.%20By%20then%20I%20was%20in%20my%20third%20trimester%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-does-birth-feel-like-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapproaching%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20on%20my%20mind.%20And%20my%20phone%20knew%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20realized%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20I%20was%20watching%20the%20kind%20of%20video%20that%20will%20be%20immediately%20recognizable%20to%20anyone%20who's%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fpregnancy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epregnant%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20age%20of%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok.%20In%20it%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bbirth%20trainer%26quot%3B%20demonstrates%20the%20appropriate%20way%20to%20relax%20while%20pregnant.%20Apparently%2C%20I%20should%20be%20sitting%20upright%2C%20feet%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20with%20hips%20open%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20better%20yet%2C%20in%20butterfly%20pose%20%E2%80%94%20to%20ensure%20my%20baby%20could%20get%20%26quot%3Boptimally%26quot%3B%20positioned%20for%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20throw%20my%20phone%20across%20the%20room.%20I%20was%20exhausted%2C%20damn%20it.%20Why%20couldn't%20I%20just%20curl%20up%20on%20the%20couch%20and%20turn%20off%20my%20brain%20for%20a%20moment%3F%20Why%20did%20every%20single%20thing%20I%20did%20have%20to%20be%20tailored%20to%20my%20pregnancy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lure%20of%20optimization%20was%20impossible%20to%20resist.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20that%20mom%20who%20aces%20every%20aspect%20of%20childbirth%2C%20bringing%20my%20child%20into%20the%20world%20in%20the%20best%20possible%20way.%20So%20I%20sat%20up%2C%20placed%20my%20feet%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20opened%20my%20hips%2C%20and%20exhaled.%20And%20I%20wasn't%20the%20only%20Good%20Birth%20striver%20out%20there%3A%20The%20video%20had%20half%20a%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20scroll%20through%20social%20media%20as%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20is%20to%20be%20told%20that%20there%20are%20a%20million%20things%20you%20should%20be%20doing%20to%20optimize%20the%20birth%20experience.%20I'm%20not%20talking%20about%20the%20common-sense%20basics%2C%20from%20birth%20education%20classes%20to%20making%20a%20birth%20plan.%20In%20a%20country%20with%20a%20sky-high%20rate%20of%20maternal%20mortality%2C%20we%20desperately%20need%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20ensuring%20the%20health%20of%20pregnant%20women.%20What%20I'm%20talking%20about%20is%20the%20growing%20cottage%20industry%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Finfluencers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirthing%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20market%20their%20preferred%20birthing%20styles%20through%20sponsored%20posts%2C%20consulting%20services%2C%20and%20online%20courses.%20There%20are%20advocates%20of%20everything%20from%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20birth%20(minimal%20intervention%20and%20no%20epidurals)%2C%20%26quot%3Becstatic%26quot%3B%20birth%20(achieved%20through%20hypnosis%20and%20other%20mental%20gymnastics)%2C%20%26quot%3Btotal%20control%26quot%3B%20birth%20(meaning%20a%20scheduled%20C-section)%2C%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-free-birth-is-dangerous-tiktok-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20birth%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20(one%20that%20happens%20outside%20the%20medical%20or%20midwifery%20systems).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20talk%20around%20optimizing%20birth%20is%20well-meaning.%20But%20it%20also%20feeds%20an%20absurd%20narrative%20that%20childbirth%20can%20be%20%3Cem%3Emastered%3C%2Fem%3E.%20How%20we%20give%20birth%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20we%20%3Cem%3Ethink%3C%2Fem%3E%20we'll%20give%20birth%20before%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eour%20due%20date%20arrives%20and%20reality%20takes%20over%20%E2%80%94%20has%20become%20the%20latest%20way%20we%20define%2C%20and%20judge%2C%20ourselves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20a%20moment%20that%20is%20inherently%20fraught%20with%20anxiety%2C%20the%20Gospel%20of%20the%20Good%20Birth%20gives%20expectant%20parents%20one%20more%20thing%20to%20be%20anxious%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20pregnancy%20content%20is%20part%20of%20this%20initiation%20into%20contemporary%20parenting%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rebecca%20Silber%2C%20who%20works%20in%20marketing%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20is%20pregnant%20with%20her%20second%20child.%20%26quot%3BIt%20starts%20with%20'I%20do%20natural%20birth'%20or%20'I'm%20an%20epidural%20mom'%20and%20then%20turns%20into%20'I%20sleep%20train'%20or%20'I'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgentle-parenting-bust-millennial-parents-helicopter-kids-misbehave-permissive-authoritative-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egentle%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E.'%26quot%3B%20What%20has%20long%20been%20a%20war%20over%20the%20best%20way%20to%20raise%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20identity%20that%20comes%20with%20choosing%20one%20parenting%20style%20over%20another%20%E2%80%94%20now%20precedes%20the%20child's%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20expectant%20parents%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20embracing%20one%20birthing%20style%20over%20another%20is%20about%20asserting%20control.%20Or%2C%20more%20precisely%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eillusion%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20control%20during%20one%20of%20life's%20most%20emotionally%20charged%2C%20high-stakes%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Megan%20Nash%2C%20a%20physical%20therapist%20assistant%20in%20Roanoke%2C%20Virginia%2C%20was%20preparing%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20her%20daughter%2C%20she%20followed%20birth%20influencers%20who%20advocated%20breathing%20work%20and%20mantras%20to%20control%20the%20pain%20of%20childbirth%2C%20free%20of%20medication.%20She%20conjured%20up%20the%20sort%20of%20gently%20lit%20images%20familiar%20to%20her%20from%20her%20Instagram%20feed%20%E2%80%94%20teary-eyed%2C%20beaming%20women%20staring%20in%20wonder%20as%20they%20cradle%20their%20newborns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20envisioned%20this%20wonderful%2C%20natural%2C%20empowering%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20that's%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20possible%2C%20based%20on%20what%20I%20was%20seeing%20on%20social%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20reality%20of%20labor%20hit%20her.%20She%20wound%20up%20asking%20for%20an%20epidural%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20that%20brought%20immediate%20physical%20relief%20but%20left%20her%20with%20the%20nagging%20feeling%20that%20she%20had%20failed%20herself%20and%20her%20baby%20girl.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20shame%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20if%20I%20couldn't%20be%20chill%20about%20it%2C%20and%20do%20it%20without%20the%20help%2C%20it%20showed%20some%20type%20of%20weakness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guilt%20trailed%20her%20home%20from%20the%20hospital.%20When%20her%20newborn%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20colicky%2C%20fussy%20baby%2C%20Nash%20came%20across%20a%20post%20that%20equated%20epidurals%20with%20giving%20your%20baby%20fentanyl.%20It%20was%20a%20completely%20bogus%20claim%2C%20but%20she%20worried%20that%20her%20daughter's%20fussiness%20might%20be%20her%20fault.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20she%20met%20another%20mom%20who%20was%20facing%20similar%20struggles%2C%20but%20who'd%20had%20an%20unmedicated%20home%20birth%2C%20that%20Nash%20accepted%20what%20her%20pediatrician%20had%20been%20telling%20her%3A%20Everything%20was%20fine.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20realized%20that%20even%20if%20I'd%20done%20everything%20differently%2C%20the%20outcome%20easily%20could%20have%20been%20exactly%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20Nash%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20freeing%20to%20think%20maybe%20I%20didn't%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sarah%20Denney%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20Indianapolis%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Boptimal%26quot%3B%20childbirth%20experience%20meant%20lying%20on%20her%20side.%20She'd%20saved%20a%20dozen%20videos%20from%20Instagram%20that%20convinced%20her%20that%20a%20side%20birth%20would%20reduce%20tearing%20and%20make%20recovery%20quicker%20than%20lying%20on%20her%20back.%20But%20that's%20not%20how%20it%20worked%20out.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20agony%2C%20lying%20on%20my%20side%2C%20pushing%2C%20with%20one%20of%20my%20legs%20lifted%20straight%20in%20the%20air%2C%20just%20dangling%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20tore%20anyway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20those%20who%20feel%20good%20about%20their%20choices%20wind%20up%20fretting%20over%20whether%20they%20got%20it%20wrong.%20Shannon%20Wolfman%2C%20a%20mother%20in%20Indianapolis%20who%20ended%20up%20having%20a%20C-section%2C%20doesn't%20regret%20having%20the%20procedure%2C%20but%20social%20media%20made%20her%20worry%20that%20she%20had%20interrupted%20the%20natural%20process%20of%20postpartum%20bonding%20by%20subjecting%20herself%20and%20her%20baby%20to%20medical%20intervention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObjectively%2C%20I%20know%20I%20made%20the%20right%20call%20in%20the%20moment%20by%20moving%20ahead%20with%20the%20C-section%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolfman%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20comparison%20game%2C%20both%20online%20and%20just%20in%20general%2C%20is%20so%20intense.%26quot%3B%20Doing%20the%20right%20thing%2C%20in%20the%20age%20of%20Instagram%2C%20is%20no%20protection%20against%20the%20fear%20of%20having%20done%20the%20wrong%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-women-allege-coolsculpting-left-them-disfigured-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrite%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20women's%20health%20for%20a%20living%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20me%20from%20falling%20prey%20to%20the%20Gospel%20of%20the%20Good%20Birth.%20My%20addiction%20to%20Instagram%20hasn't%20just%20given%20me%20anxiety%20about%20my%20coming%20labor%20%E2%80%94%20it%20also%20has%20me%20relitigating%20my%20first%20experience%20giving%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20not%20tethered%20to%20social%20media%20would%20conclude%20that%20my%20first%20birth%20went%20fine.%20As%20my%20pregnancy%20progressed%2C%20I%20read%20a%20handful%20of%20books%2C%20practiced%20meditation%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20staying%20calm%20during%20painful%20contractions%2C%20and%20made%20flash-card%20reminders%20about%20labor%20positions%20and%20breathing%20techniques%20to%20take%20with%20me%20to%20the%20hospital.%20My%20water%20broke%20right%20on%20time%2C%20and%20my%20partner%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoula-advice-things-pregnant-people-should-know-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20doula%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20me%20at%20the%20hospital.%20My%20labor%2C%20which%20took%2022%20hours%2C%20was%20the%20hardest%2C%20most%20shocking%20physical%20experience%20of%20my%20life%2C%20even%20with%20an%20epidural.%20But%20I%20delivered%20a%20healthy%20baby%20girl%2C%20and%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20hospital%20happier%20than%20I'd%20ever%20been%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20social%20media%20has%20me%20second-guessing%20the%20whole%20experience.%20A%20few%20days%20after%20Instagram%20yanked%20me%20up%20from%20the%20couch%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20going%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20unfounded%20claims%20linking%20medical%20interventions%20during%20delivery%20with%20bonding%20issues%20later%20in%20life.%20A%20wave%20of%20panic%20washed%20over%20me%20as%20I%20remembered%20how%2C%20after%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feldest-daughter-syndrome-big-sister-responsibility-siblings-babysitting-childcare-2024-9%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dbusiness-sf%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwY2xjawHjmeZleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHeJuKQkWwQcQA0ff50_iDWRzwXUv1Z5TIaU0zVEYgC4xArHcPK4oDrHL7w_aem_vffukK2kF_27U9-1WL9p2w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewborn%20daughter%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20placed%20on%20my%20chest%2C%20a%20few%20minutes%20passed%20before%20I%20was%20able%20to%20interact%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mind%20jumped%20to%20the%20present.%20When%20my%20daughter%20catches%20me%20walking%20off%20to%20grab%20something%20or%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20she%20sometimes%20gets%20upset%20and%20yells%2C%20%26quot%3BMommy!%20You%20forgot%20me!%26quot%3B%20Had%20my%20decision%20to%20get%20an%20epidural%20short-circuited%20our%20bond%2C%20dooming%20her%20to%20an%20anxious%20attachment%20style%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20zero%20evidence%20it%20had.%20When%20Nash%2C%20the%20physical%20therapist%2C%20shared%20a%20similar%20worry%20with%20me%2C%20I'd%20recognized%20immediately%20that%20her%20natural%20anxiety%20as%20a%20mother%20had%20been%20amplified%20to%20an%20excruciating%20level%20by%20the%20idiocy%20of%20social%20media.%20But%20there%20I%20was%2C%20crying%20over%20the%20dishes%2C%20worried%20that%20I%20had%20failed%20as%20a%20mother.%20My%20big%2C%20heaving%20sobs%20drowned%20out%20the%20sounds%20from%20the%20baby%20monitor%20on%20the%20counter%20%E2%80%94%20my%20toddler%20upstairs%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20giddily%20splashing%20around%