aid%20she's%20required%20to%20work%20in%20person%20between%20one%20and%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20year.%20She%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshe%20currently%20goes%20in%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20in%20the%20summer%20it%20was%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColvin%20is%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-supercommuters-travel-across-multiple-states-for-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercommuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20making%20long%20trips%20to%20work.%20A%20Stanford%20University%20study%20published%20in%20June%20defined%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnbloom.people.stanford.edu%2Fsites%2Fg%2Ffiles%2Fsbiybj24291%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Ffile%2Fsupercommuters_final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercommuter%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20anyone%20with%20a%20journey%20of%20more%20than%2075%20miles.%20The%20share%20of%20supercommutes%20in%20the%2010%20largest%20US%20cities%20was%2032%25%20greater%20between%20November%202023%20and%20February%20than%20between%20the%20same%20time%20period%20four%20years%20prior%2C%20per%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20increase%20was%20likely%20driven%20by%20the%20uptick%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-americans-super-commuting-75-miles-work-wfh-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20working%20arrangements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20the%20study.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20Americans%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-regretting-moves-from-city-to-suburbs-housing-crisis-millennials-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eduring%20the%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-americans-move-from-cities-rural-areas-millennials-gen-x-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20housing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20decided%20they%20could%20stomach%20a%20long%20commute%20when%20their%20employers%20later%20called%20them%20back%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20commuting%20day%2C%20Colvin%20said%20she%20wakes%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%2C%20catches%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-prepare-for-long-train-rides-problems-frequent-traveler-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmtrak%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20an%20hour%20later%20at%20Baltimore%20Penn%20Station%2C%20arrives%20at%20Moynihan%20Train%20Hall%20in%20New%20York%20around%208%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20and%20gets%20to%20the%20office%2030%20minutes%20later.%20She%20leaves%20work%20around%205%3A45%20p.m.%20and%20is%20home%20by%209%20p.m.%20When%20she%20has%20to%20commute%20the%20next%20day%2C%20she%20tries%20to%20be%20asleep%20by%2011%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20hard%20commute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2023-year-old%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20it's%20a%20commute%20Colvin%20said%20worthwhile%2C%20in%20part%20because%20being%20in%20New%20York%20helps%20her%20pursue%20a%20second%20career%20as%20an%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f000822-eec9-419f-bd5d-fbf0e21c1b9e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalancing%20challenges%20with%20opportunities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EColvin%20said%20moving%20to%20the%20Big%20Apple%20has%20made%20it%20much%20easier%20for%20her%20to%20attend%20acting%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eauditions%2C%20and%20that%20she's%20booked%20three%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20two%20of%20which%20required%20her%20to%20live%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20said%20Manhattan's%20prominent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-streets-culture-is-contributing-to-the-loneliness-crisis-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinance%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20who%20works%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20York%20City%20was%20always%20the%20end%20goal%20for%20both%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20timing%20was%20admittedly%20sooner%20than%20expected%2C%20but%20it%20was%20an%20opportunity%20that%20ultimately%20made%20sense%20for%20both%20our%20careers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20moving%20to%20New%20York%20City%20has%20helped%20Colvin%20supplement%20her%20salary%20with%20earnings%20from%20acting%20gigs%2C%20she%20said%20it's%20also%20had%20some%20financial%20downsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20New%20York%20City%20is%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-starting-salaries-cities-cost-of-living-nyc-austin-atlanta-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20expensive%20places%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Colvin%20thinks%20she%20might%20have%20a%20higher%20salary%20if%20her%20job%20were%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City%20rather%20than%20Baltimore%3A%20She%20said%20she%20earns%20less%20than%20%24100%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20paying%20a%20premium%20on%20bills%20and%20taxes%20to%20live%20in%20New%20York%20while%20only%20collecting%20a%20Baltimore%20salary%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommuting%20costs%20have%20also%20impacted%20her%20finances.%20Colvin%20said%20she%20used%20to%20buy%20a%20multi-ride%20Amtrak%20pass%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20to%20reduce%20her%20per-ticket%20cost%20and%20not%20be%20locked%20into%20a%20specific%20train.%20But%20since%20Amtrak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeswv.com%2Fnews%2Fnational_news%2Famtrak-raises-prices-on-northeast-corridor-multi-ride-tickets%2Farticle_d2250338-4537-11ef-9d20-4ff7747177a2.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20prices%20on%20multi-ride%20tickets%20for%20the%20Northeast%20Corridor%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethis%20year%2C%20she%20said%20this%20option%20no%20longer%20made%20financial%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2010-ride%20ticket%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Baltimore%20costs%20%24750%2C%20while%20a%20monthly%20ticket%20(valid%20for%20up%20to%20two%20trips%20a%20day%20in%20one%20calendar%20month)%20costs%20%241%2C875.%20In%20comparison%2C%20Colvin%20said%20buying%20tickets%20individually%20typically%20costs%20between%20%2435%20and%20%2450%20per%20round-trip%20ticket%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20often%20amounted%20to%20less%20than%20%24500%20a%20month%20in%20combined%20ticket%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20multi-ride%20pass%20offers%20more%20flexibility%2C%20but%20at%20least%20for%20my%20situation%2C%20is%20not%20worth%20the%20price%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColvin%20said%20she's%20reduced%20her%20commuting%20costs%20by%20buying%20tickets%20a%20few%20months%20in%20advance%20and%20taking%20advantage%20of%20Amtrak%20sales%20and%20promotions.%20Overall%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20been%20able%20to%20cover%20her%20living%20expenses%20and%20have%20some%20money%20left%20over%20for%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20downside%20of%20Colvin's%20commute%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bfatigue%26quot%3B%20that%20comes%20with%20getting%20up%20early%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20regularly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20making%20a%20three-hour%20trip%20%3Cs%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%239efcf6%5C%22%3Eregularly%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fs%3E%2C%20she%20said.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20she%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20change%20course%20or%20look%20for%20roles%20based%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20long%20commute%20to%20work%3F%20Are%20you%20willing%20to%20share%20your%20story%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuting-nyc-baltimore-amtrak-acting-career-remote-work-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider