Virat%20Kohli's%20Retirement%20Rumours%2C%20Pat%20Cummins'%20Statement%20Wins%20Internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralian%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20rates%20Virat%20Kohli%20as%20a%20great%20competitor%20who%20makes%20the%20game%20lively%20with%20his%20theatrics%20and%20he%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bsad%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20latest%20Border-Gavaskar%20trophy%20does%20end%20up%20being%20the%20Indian%20superstar's%20last%20tour%20Down%20Under.%20Following%20the%20hundred%20in%20the%20series%20opener%2C%20Kohli's%20troubles%20outside%20the%20off-stump%20compounded%20as%20he%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20slip%20cordon%20eight%20times%20over%20the%20course%20of%20five%20Tests.%20The%20tour%20that%20got%20over%20on%20Sunday%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20Kohli's%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20been%20a%20a%20wonderful%20contest.%20More%20than%20just%20the%20runs%20that%20he%20scored%2C%20he%20brings%20a%20bit%20of%20theatre%20to%20the%20game%20which%20is%20sometimes%20good%20and%20sometimes%20it%20can%20rile%20you%20up%20as%20an%20opposition%2C%20which%20I'm%20sure%20is%20part%20of%20his%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said%20in%20a%20response%20to%20a%20PTI%20query%20after%20the%20six%20wicket%20win%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20enjoyed%20playing%20with%20him.%20You%20know%2C%20he's%20been%20one%20of%20the%20the%20star%20batters%20for%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so.%20You%20know%2C%20if%20you%20get%20his%20wicket%20it%20goes%20a%20long%20way%20to%20winning%20a%20game%20so%20yeah%2C%20it%20will%20be%20sad%20if%20it's%20his%20last%20series.%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20did%20admit%20that%20Bumrah's%20absence%20on%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20series%20did%20help%20them%2C%20considering%20he%20took%2032%20wickets%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20he%20(Bumrah)%20bowled%20he%20seemed%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20and%20took%20some%20key%20wickets.%20So%20yeah%2C%20no%20doubt%20that%20(his%20absence)%20helped%20our%20chase%20a%20little%20bit.%26quot%3B%20Although%20he%20termed%20it%20as%20Indian%20team's%20internal%20matter%2C%20Cummins%20was%20a%20touch%20surprised%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20decision%20to%20drop%20himself%20from%20the%20playing%20eleven%20on%20account%20of%20poor%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20always%20surprised%20when%20the%20captain%20kind%20of%20doesn't%20play.%20And%20you%20know%2C%20same%20with%20Ashwin%20retiring%2C%20but%20honestly%20it%20doesn't%20really%20affect%20us%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20turn%20up%20and%20you%20see%20who's%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20team%20sheet%20and%20you%20play%20whoever%20eleven%20they%20put%20out%20there.%20Honestly%2C%20it's%20been%20very%20little%20conversation%20I've%20chatted%20with%20him%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20termed%20the%20win%20against%20India%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuge%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Indo-Australia%20bilaterals%2C%20having%20lost%20twice%20at%20home%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it's%20a%20huge%20win%20in%20the%20context%20of%20this%20series.%20It's%20as%20big%20a%20series%20as%20you%20get%20to%20play%20at%20home.%20It%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20kind%20of%20see-sawing%20throughout%20the%20whole%20series.%20So%20to%20finish%20it%203-1%20to%20hold%20the%20trophy%20is%20an%20amazing%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B......%20and%20I%20think%20the%20extra%20layer%20is%20now%20securing%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20Final%20which%20was%20always%20a%20huge%20goal%20for%20us%20in%20this%20cycle.%26quot%3B%20He%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20T20%20World%20Cup%20winning%20squad%2C%20won%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%2C%20World%20Test%20Championship%20mace%20and%20Ashes%20as%20the%20skipper%20and%20now%20the%20India%20series%20that%20his%20predecessor%20Tim%20Paine%20had%20lost%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20has%20any%20succession%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20he%20sidestepped%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%20I%20just%20absolutely%20love%20what%20I%20do.%20So%2C%20I%20mean%20that's%20probably%20the%20biggest%20driver%20in%20wanting%20to%20play%20Test%20Cricket%20and%20work%20with%20this%20team%20and%20support%20staff.%26quot%3B%20So%20does%20he%20feel%20that%20he%20has%20done%20it%20all%3F%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20I%20have%20got%20to%20keep%20playing.%20We'll%20stay%20on%20this%20side%20guys%20and%20then%20we'll%20come%20over%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20smiled%20and%20everyone%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736063820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmh4juphg_pat-cummins-and-virat-kohli_625x300_05_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fon-virat-kohlis-retirement-rumours-pat-cummins-statement-wins-internet-7403678%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australian%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20rates%20Virat%20Kohli%20as%20a%20great%20competitor%20who%20makes%20the%20game%20lively%20with%20his%20theatrics%20and%20he%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bsad%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20latest%20Border-Gavaskar%20trophy%20does%20end%20up%20being%20the%20Indian%20superstar's%20last%20tour%20Down%20Under%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fon-virat-kohlis-retirement-rumours-pat-cummins-statement-wins-internet-7403678%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhaya%20Kadam%20suggested%20the%20song%20%E2%80%98%20Daiya%20Yeh%20Main%20Kahan%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A173606372