20Meerut%20South%2C%20featuring%20nine%20stations%2C%20is%20operational.%20With%20this%20inauguration%2C%20the%20operational%20stretch%20of%20the%20Namo%20Bharat%20corridor%20will%20expand%20to%2055%20km%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%2011%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi-Meerut%20Travel%20Time%20Reduced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20commencement%20of%20operations%20on%20this%20section%2C%20Meerut%20is%20now%20directly%20connected%20to%20Delhi.%20This%20will%20reduce%20travel%20time%20by%20one-third%2C%20enabling%20commuters%20to%20travel%20from%20New%20Ashok%20Nagar%20to%20Meerut%20South%20in%20just%20under%2040%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20Vihar%20underground%20station%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20stations%20on%20the%20Namo%20Bharat%20corridor.%20Commuters%20will%20be%20able%20to%20travel%20from%20here%20to%20Meerut%20South%20in%20just%2035%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20special%20arrangement%20for%20the%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20and%20pedestrians%20at%20this%20station%2C%20three%20bridges%20have%20been%20built%20over%20the%20Ghazipur%20drain.%20Two%20of%20these%20bridges%20are%20to%20be%20used%20for%20vehicle%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20while%20one%20is%20exclusively%20for%20pedestrians%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Ashok%20Nagar%20is%20the%20first%20elevated%20Namo%20Bharat%20station%20to%20be%20operational%20on%20the%20Delhi%20section.%20Here%2C%20the%20corridor%20crosses%20the%20New%20Ashok%20Nagar%20metro%20station%20at%20a%20height%20of%2020%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20train%20services%2C%20a%20commercial%20centre%20has%20also%20been%20planned%20at%20the%20station%20for%20the%20convenience%20of%20commuters.%20This%20station%20is%20being%20connected%20to%20the%20Blue%20Line%20of%20Delhi%20Metro%20through%20a%2090-meter-long%20foot%20over%20bridge%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Namo%20Bharat%20trains%20have%20served%20over%2050%20lakh%20com