that%20there%20were%20so%20many%20reports%20written%20and%20things%20said%2C%20I%20mean%20you%20could%20be%20more%20sensible%20about%20it.%20When%20a%20captain%20or%20a%20leader%20takes%20a%20call%2C%20keeping%20the%20team%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20anything%20bad.%20A%20lot%20of%20things%20have%20been%20said%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20individuals%20are%20there%2C%20but%20most%20importantly%2C%20there%20is%20the%20team%20and%20the%20country.%20I%20think%20all%20players%20should%20keep%20the%20team%20ahead%20of%20their%20individual%20interests.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20showed%20accountability%20at%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20press%20conference%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20Bumrah's%20absence%20from%20the%20entire%20second%20innings%20due%20to%20a%20back%20issue.%20The%20head%20coach%20admitted%20that%20it%20would've%20been%20nice%20if%20the%20pacer%20was%20available%20but%20the%20team%20isn't%20dependent%20on%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20have%20been%20nice%20if%20he%20would%20have%20been%20there%2C%20but%20we%20still%20had%20five%20bowlers%2C%20and%20a%20good%20team%20is%20one%20which%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20one%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736060100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1j8jq46o_gautam-gambhir-pc-x_625x300_05_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fyou-could-be-more-sensible-gautam-gambhir-left-fuming-at-reporter-over-rohit-sharma-question-7403423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20wasn't%20happy%20when%20a%20reporter%20asked%20about%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20decision%20to%20skip%20the%20Sydney%20Test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A119%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fyou-could-be-more-sensible-gautam-gambhir-left-fuming-at-report