ghs-journey-to-becoming-the-worlds-highest-paid-employee-in-electric-vehicles%2Farticleshow%2F116932008.cms%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20exceptional%20salary%20package%20includes%20stock%20options%20valued%20at%20approximately%20%242.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20holds%20a%20BTech%20degree%20from%20Stanford%20University%20and%20an%20MBA%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20He%20began%20his%20career%20at%20well-known%20firms%20like%20HP%20(Hewlett-Packard)%20and%20Sun%20Microsystems%2C%20and%20later%20went%20on%20to%20found%20multiple%20startups%2C%20with%20one%20of%20his%20early%20ventures%20being%20AirSoft%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20in%20various%20companies%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20founded%20QuantumScape%20in%202010%2C%20a%20company%20that%20has%20since%20focused%20on%20breakthrough%20innovations%2C%20particularly%20in%20battery%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantumScape%20is%20developing%20solid-state%20batteries%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20These%20are%20different%20from%20traditional%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20because%20they%20don't%20use%20liquid%20electrolytes.%20This%20makes%20them%20safer%2C%20allows%20for%20faster%20charging%2C%20and%20increases%20energy%20density.%20These%20improvements%20help%20solve%20key%20issues%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20such%20as%20range%20anxiety%20and%20long%20charging%20times%2C%20making%20the%20batteries%20a%20better%20option%20for%20the%20future%20of%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20support%20from%20investors%20like%20Bill%20Gates%20and%20Volkswagen%2C%20QuantumScape%20is%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20transportation.%20Under%20Mr%20Singh's%20leadership%2C%20Quantumscape%20is%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20EV%20battery%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%202024%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20stepped%20down%20as%20QuantumScape's%20CEO%2C%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20Siva%20Sivaram.%20Mr%20Sivaram%20had%20joined%20the%20company%20as%20President%20in%20September%202023.%20Jagdeep%20Singh%20still%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.quantumscape.com%2Fresources%2Fpress-releases%2Fnews-details%2F2024%2FQuantumScape-Appoints-Dr.-Siva-Sivaram-as-CEO-to-Lead-Next-Phase-of-Growth%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinues%20as%20Chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Board.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BStealth%20Startup%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20per%20his%20LinkedIn%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736058360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmhnno288_jagdeep-singh_625x300_05_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjagdeep-singh-this-indian-origin-techie-earns-rs-48-crore-a-day-what-he-does-at-quantumscape-7403291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jagdeep%20Singh's%20exceptional%20salary%20package%20includes%20stock%20options%20valued%20at%20approximately%20%242.3%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjagdeep-singh-this-indian-origin-techie-earns-rs-48-crore-a-day-what-he-does-at-quantumscape-7403291%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hollywood's%20most%20explosive%20divorces%20that%20shook%20tinseltown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736058317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116960068%2Cimgsize-44058.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fjohnny-depp-and-amber-heard-brad-pitt-and-angelina-jolie-hollywoods-messiest-divorces%2Fphotostory%2F116960068.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2