ration%20of%20Syria's%20political%20and%20military%20elite%20provided%20intelligence%20crucial%20to%20Israel's%20success%20in%20the%201967%20Six-Day%20War.%20Despite%20decades%20of%20attempts%2C%20the%20location%20of%20Cohen's%20burial%20site%20is%20undisclosed%2C%20with%20Syrian%20authorities%20reportedly%20relocating%20his%20body%20multiple%20times%20to%20prevent%20their%20retrieval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECohen%20was%20born%20in%201924%20in%20Alexandria%2C%20Egypt%2C%20to%20a%20family%20of%20Egyptian%20Jews.%20Following%20the%20establishment%20of%20Israel%20in%201948%2C%20Cohen's%20family%20immigrated%20to%20the%20newly%20founded%20state.%20Cohen%20himself%20followed%20in%201957%2C%20after%20years%20of%20Zionist%20activism%20that%20reportedly%20included%20aiding%20the%20covert%20migration%20of%20Egyptian%20Jews%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20in%20Israeli%20military%20intelligence%2C%20Cohen%20was%20recruited%20by%20Mossad%20in%20the%20early%201960s.%20Using%20his%20fluency%20in%20Arabic%2C%20Spanish%2C%20and%20French%2C%20Mossad%20crafted%20an%20elaborate%20cover%20identity%20for%20Cohen.%20He%20became%20Kamel%20Amin%20Thaabet%2C%20a%20Syrian%20businessman%20whose%20family%20had%20emigrated%20to%20Argentina.%20Cohen%20relocated%20to%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20where%20he%20ingrained%20himself%20within%20the%20Arab%20and%20Syrian%20diasporas%2C%20gaining%20trust%20and%20access%20that%20would%20later%20prove%20critical%20to%20his%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201962%2C%20Cohen%20moved%20to%20Damascus%20under%20his%20assumed%20identity%2C%20where%20he%20quickly%20ascended%20to%20prominence%20within%20Syrian%20society.%20Known%20for%20hosting%20lavish%20parties%20attended%20by%20influential%20political%20and%20military%20figures%2C%20Cohen%20used%20these%20gatherings%20to%20extract%20valuable%20intelligence.%20His%20efforts%20yielded%20detailed%20information%20about%20Syrian%20fortifications%20in%20the%20Golan%20Heights%2C%20later%20aiding%20Israel's%20capture%20of%20the%20territory%20in%20the%20Six-Day%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECohen's%20espionage%20activities%2C%20however%2C%20came%20to%20an%20abrupt%20end%20in%201965.%20Syrian%20intelligence%2C%20with%20assistance%20from%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20identified%20his%20covert%20radio%20transmissions%20to%20Israel.%20On%20January%2024%2C%201965%2C%20Syrian%20authorities%20raided%20his%20home.%20Cohen%20was%20arrested%2C%20tried%2C%20and%20convicted%20of%20espionage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20international%20pleas%20for%20clemency%2C%20Cohen%20was%20publicly%20hanged%20on%20May%2018%2C%201965.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20execution%2C%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20Cohen's%20body%20have%20been%20a%20source%20of%20contention.%20Syria%20has%20consistently%20refused%20Israeli%20requests%20to%20repatriate%20his%20body%2C%20rejecting%20multiple%20offers%20of%20prisoner%20exchanges.%20Syrian%20officials%20have%20admitted%20to%20relocating%20it%20multiple%20times%20to%20thwart%20Israeli%20recovery%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Mossad%20successfully%20retrieved%20Cohen's%20wristwatch%20from%20Syria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20the%20Assad%20regime%20in%20parts%20of%20Syria%20has%20created%20new%20opportunities%20for%20negotiation.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20including%20Mossad%20Director%20David%20Barnea%2C%20are%20directly%20involved%20in%20talks%20with%20former%20members%20of%20the%20Assad%20government.%20These%20discussions%20are%20reportedly%20facilitated%20by%20Russian%20mediators.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736055300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fgduca9m8_eli-cohen-mossad-spy-_625x300_05_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmossad-spy-was-publicly-hanged-by-syria-in-1965-israel-wants-his-body-back-7403157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Businessman%20Kamel%20Amin%20Thaabet%20arrived%20in%20the%20Syrian%20capital%20of%20D