%20on%20most%20kinds%20of%20alcohol%20has%20declined%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-spending-trends-gen-z-millennials-baby-boomers-surgeon-general-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20adults%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYounger%20consumers%20under%20the%20age%20of%2030%20have%20become%20progressively%20less%20likely%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20to%20drink%20alcohol%20at%20all%2C%20with%2062%25%20of%20adults%20under%20age%2035%20saying%20they%20drink%2C%20down%20from%2072%25%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F509690%2Fyoung-adults-drinking-less-prior-decades.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGallup%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20brands%20have%20launched%20non-alcoholic%20options%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20market%20that%2C%20while%20they%20don't%20want%20a%20boozy%20drink%2C%20may%20still%20want%20something%20new%20to%20indulge%20in%20on%20a%20special%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeineken%20first%20released%20its%20non-alcoholic%20beer%2C%20Heineken%200.0%2C%20in%20March%202017%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20Germany%2C%20expanding%20its%20release%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorona%20Sunbrew%200.0%25%20debuted%20in%202022%2C%20a%20product%20from%20Constellation%20Brands%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20beverage%20company%20that%20produces%20beer%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20spirits%20from%20brands%20like%20Modelo%20and%20Corona%20Extra.%20AB%20InBev%2C%20which%20produces%20drinks%20for%20500%20global%20brands%20including%20Budweiser%20and%20Michelob%20Ultra%2C%20launched%20Corona%20Cero%20the%20same%20year.%20Constellation%20Brands%20owns%20the%20US%20brand%20licenses%20for%20Corona%20beer%20in%20the%20US%2C%20while%20AB%20InBev%20owns%20the%20beer%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20their%20zero-proof%20bets%20are%20paying%20off%2C%20executives%20have%20said%20in%20recent%20earning%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarold%20van%20den%20Broek%2C%20Heineken's%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%2C%20said%20during%20an%20October%202024%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20an%20acceleration%20in%20non-alcoholic%20sales%20across%20many%20markets%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20brand's%20non-alcoholic%20options%20have%20grown%20to%20over%204%25%20of%20their%20total%20portfolio%20since%20launching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20believe%20that%20this%20category%2C%20which%20has%20been%20growing%20about%206%25%20on%20average%20since%202018%2C%20will%20continue%20this%20growth%20trajectory%2C%26quot%3B%20van%20den%20Broek%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20high%20hopes%20for%20the%20non-alcohol%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstellation%20Brands'%20president%20and%20CEO%2C%20William%20Newlands%2C%20shared%20a%20similar%20optimism.%20During%20an%20April%2024%2C%202024%20earnings%20call%2C%20he%20said%20Corona%20Non-Alcoholic%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20number%20one%20share%20gainer%20in%20the%20non-alcoholic%20segment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20does%20reflect%20some%20change%20in%20consumer%20behavior%20or%20people%20that%20are%20concerned%20about%20being%20the%20designated%20driver%20but%20still%20want%20to%20enjoy%20an%20outstanding-tasting%20beer%2C%26quot%3B%20Newlands%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20emphasize%20the%20betterment%20trends%20as%20we%20go%20forward%20with%20a%20number%20of%20our%20product%20offerings%20and%20certainly%20expect%20Corona%20Non-Alcoholic%20to%20continue%20to%20grow%20here%20in%20this%20coming%20fiscal%20year%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel%20Doukeris%2C%20AB%20InBev's%20CEO%2C%20likewise%20told%20investors%20during%20an%20October%2021%2C%202024%2C%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20views%20the%20non-alcohol%20beer%20segment%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20key%20opportunity%20to%20develop%20new%20beer%20consumption%20occasions%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20development%20in%20this%20market%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20focus%20of%20the%20company's%20strategy%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20gained%20market%20share%20of%20non-alcohol%20beer%20in%20over%2060%25%20of%20our%20key%20markets%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20with%20Corona%20Cero%20more%20than%20doubling%20both%20volumes%20and%20revenues%2C%26quot%3B%20Doukeris%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20no-alcohol%20beer%20is%20currently%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20our%20global%20volume%2C%20we%20believe%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20for%20incremental%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20representatives%20have%20long%20warned%20of%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkglobalhealth.org%2Farticle%2Falcohol-industry-panics-healthier-habits-cut-sales%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20on%20alcohol%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20a%20warning%20which%20increased%20in%20fervor%20after%20the%20late%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Feurope%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F06-11-2023-joint-statement-by-who-europe-and-iarc-to-the-european-parliament---raising-awareness-of-the-link-between-alcohol-and-cancer%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThere%2520is%2520also%2520clear%2520evidence%2Cfor%2520cancers%2520can%2520be%2520established.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorld%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20indicated%20even%20low%20levels%20of%20alcohol%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20cancer%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20safe%20amount%20of%20alcohol%20consumption%20for%20cancers%20and%20health%20can%20be%20established.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20amid%20the%20concern%20that%20alcohol%20sales%20might%20dwindle%2C%20brands%20have%20begun%20to%20capitalize%20on%20shifting%20consumer%20behaviors%20and%20buoy%20their%20overall%20revenue.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcg.com%2Fpublications%2F2024%2Fsober-curious-non-alcoholic-drinks-industry-is-toasting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20values%20the%20global%20market%20share%20of%20no-or-low-alcoholic%20beers%2C%20wines%2C%20and%20spirits%20at%20more%20than%20%2413%20billion%2C%20with%20sales%20expected%20to%20grow%20at%20an%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20over%207%25%20between%202023%20and%202027%2C%20settling%20at%20about%204%25%20of%20the%20overall%20alcohol%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEliott%20Edge%2C%20the%20bar%20manager%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-hekate-zero-alcohol-sober-bar-nyc-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHekate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20New%20York%20City's%20only%20sober%20bar%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20whole%20ecosystem%26quot%3B%20of%20new%20non-alcoholic%20offerings%20that%20customers%20are%20clamoring%20for%2C%20having%20witnessed%20increasing%20demand%20for%20the%20alcohol-free%20options%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20the%20sober%2C%20the%20sober-curious%2C%20and%20folks%20who%20still%20drink%20but%20want%20to%20take%20a%20break%20for%20one%20reason%20or%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Edge%20said.%20%26quot%3BLocals%2C%20tourists%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20wants%20to%20see%20what%20it's%20like.%20So%20the%20non-alcoholic%20options%20don't%20cater%20specifically%20to%20any%20particular%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20more%20and%20more%20bars%20and%20brands%20are%20going%20to%20offer%20non-alcoholic%20options%20going%20forward%2C%20Edge%20predicted%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they're%20going%20to%20realize%20that%20it's%20like%20vegetarians%20or%20vegans%20or%20gluten-free%20or%20dairy-free.%20It's%20just%20another%20type%20of%20customer%20profile%20to%20cater%20to%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20ones%20that%20don't%20cater%20to%20that%20are%20going%20to%20go%20the%20way%20of%20the%20dinosaur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-brands-preparing-growing-nonalcoholic-market-heineken-constellation-anheuser-busch-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736042099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6779ca969fc2c160094732b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-brands-preparing-growing-nonalcoholic-market-heineken-constellation-anheuser-busch-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alcohol%20companies%20like%20Heineken%2C%20Constellation%20Brands%2C%20and%20AB%20InBev%20have%20been%20preparing%20for%20a%20customer%20culture%20shift%20toward%20nonalcoholic%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A136%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-brands-preparing-growing-nonalcoholic-market-heineken-constellation-anheuser-busch-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Most%20evil%20man%E2%80%99%20George%20Soros%20gets%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20Presidential%20Medal%20of%20freedom%3A%20Fox%20%26amp%3B%20Friends%20reacts%20with%20fury%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736041495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116956240%2Cimgsize-793658.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmost-evil-man-george-soros-gets-bidens-presidential-medal-of-freedom-fox-friends-reacts-with-fury%2Farticleshow%2F116955535.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116955535.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engageme