z%20an%20%26quot%3Bincompetent%20fool%26quot%3B%20and%20signaled%20his%20support%20for%20Germany's%20AfD%20party.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20new%20interview%2C%20Scholz%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20Musk%20backing%20the%20AfD.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20responded%20to%20criticism%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-afd-germany-far-right-party-immigration-election-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20a%20German%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%20published%20in%20Stern%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Scholz%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20new%26quot%3B%20about%20criticism%20from%20%26quot%3Brich%20media%20entrepreneurs%20who%20do%20not%20appreciate%20social%20democratic%20politics%20and%20do%20not%20hide%20their%20opinions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20your%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20people%20on%20social%20media%20who%20want%20to%20attract%20attention%20with%20strong%20slogans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20is%3A%20Don't%20feed%20the%20troll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20concerning%26quot%3B%20that%20Musk%20supported%20%26quot%3Ba%20partly%20far-right%20party%20like%20the%20AfD%2C%20which%20advocates%20rapprochement%20with%20Putin's%20Russia%20and%20seeks%20to%20weaken%20transatlantic%20relations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20sparked%20debate%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-in-germany-struggled-berlin-loves-living-in-dresden-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGermany%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20weeks%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sparks-backlash-germany-weighs-in-on-politics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalling%20Scholz%20an%20%26quot%3Bincompetent%20fool%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20signaling%20his%20support%20for%20AfD%2C%20the%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AfD%20was%20founded%20in%202013%20as%20an%20anti-European%20Union%20party.%20More%20recently%2C%20it%20has%20taken%20a%20hard%20line%20on%20immigration%2C%20earning%20it%20the%20label%20of%20far-right%20in%20some%20political%20corners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20set%20to%20co-lead%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20under%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20incoming%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20has%20rejected%20the%20far-right%20label%20and%20publicly%20supported%20the%20AfD%20in%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20his%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20reshared%20a%20video%20in%20December%20by%20the%20right-wing%20influencer%20Naomi%20Seibt%20in%20which%20she%20criticized%20Friedrich%20Merz%20%E2%80%94%20a%20leading%20candidate%20to%20become%20Germany's%20next%20chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20the%20AfD%20can%20save%20Germany%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%20He%20later%20reaffirmed%20his%20support%20for%20the%20AfD%20in%20an%20op-ed%20for%20the%20German%20newspaper%20Welt%20am%20Sonntag.%20Welt%20am%20Sonntag%20and%20Business%20Insider%20are%20both%20owned%20by%20Axel%20Springer%20SE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20article%2C%20Musk%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20AfD%20advocates%20a%20controlled%20immigration%20policy%20that%20gives%20priority%20to%20integration%20and%20the%20preservation%20of%20German%20culture%20and%20security.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20xenophobia%2C%20but%20about%20ensuring%20that%20Germany%20does%20not%20lose%20its%20identity%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20globalization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20German%20politicians%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20Musk's%20comments%2C%20which%20have%20come%20just%20weeks%20before%20Germany%20holds%20a%20snap%20election%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20last%20month%2C%20Germany's%20health%20minister%2C%20Karl%20Lauterbach%2C%20said%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20interfere%20in%20our%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20his%20platform%20%26quot%3Bprofits%20from%20hate%20and%20incitement%20and%20radicalizes%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20now%20due%20to%20hold%20a%20live%20discussion%20on%20January%209%20with%20Alice%20Weidel%2C%20co-leader%20of%20the%20AfD%20and%20the%20party's%20nominee%20for%20chancellor.%20The%20chat%20is%20set%20to%20be%20held%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGermany%20isn't%20the%20only%20country%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-politics-europe-reform-afd-farage-meloni-trump-elections-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20has%20shown%20his%20support%20for%20right-wing%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20criticized%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20and%20teased%20donations%20to%20the%20Reform%20Party%2C%20a%20right-wing%20populist%20party%20led%20by%20Nigel%20Farage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20also%20backed%20Italy's%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%2C%20who%20is%20also%20considered%20right-wing%2C%20calling%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bprecious%20genius%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Beven%20more%20beautiful%20on%20the%20inside%20than%20she%20is%20on%20the%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folaf-scholz-elon-musk-afd-germany-elections-troll-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736017076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677980cf59d276c1cdb00ae1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folaf-scholz-elon-musk-afd-germany-elections-troll-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Musk%20earlier%20called%20Scholz%20an%20%26quot%3Bincompetent%20fool%26qu