knew%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20be%20a%20landowner%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarbeswar%20never%20gave%20up%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20improving%20his%20situation.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20adversity%2C%20he%20made%20a%20promise%3A%20%E2%80%9CThirty%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20made%20a%20promise%20to%20myself.%20I%20saw%20landowners%20being%20respected.%20We%20had%20nothing%20to%20our%20name%20%E2%80%94%20no%20land%2C%20no%20work%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20that%20respect.%20My%20only%20goal%20was%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20earn%20my%20family%20and%20me%20that%20honour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20would%20never%20be%20a%20landowner%2C%20nor%20would%20I%20become%20extremely%20wealthy%2C%20but%20I%20promised%20myself%20I%20would%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20earn%20that%20respect.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20shaped%20me%20into%20the%20person%20I%20am%20today%20%E2%80%94%20my%20character%2C%20my%20work%2C%20and%20my%20commitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20rising%20in-state%20tensions%2C%20the%20people%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%2C%20including%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20village%2C%20began%20claiming%20forest%20land%20as%20their%20own.%20With%20no%20other%20place%20to%20farm%2C%20they%20took%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20turning%20the%20jungle%20into%20usable%20land%20for%20cultivation.%20Sarbeswar%2C%20too%2C%20became%20involved%20in%20clearing%20and%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20farming.%20He%20leased%20a%2012-acre%20plot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20a%20strong%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%20Sarbeswar%20began%20farming%20with%20traditional%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20what%20I%20saw%20other%20elders%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20growing%20eggplant%2C%20chilli%2C%20Assam%20lemon%2C%20and%20other%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20recalls.%20However%2C%20the%20methods%20proved%20insufficient%2C%20and%20the%20land%20lacked%20the%20fertility%20needed%20to%20sustain%20a%20profitable%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitial%20hurdles%20like%20inadequate%20finances%20for%20investment%20into%20agriculture%2C%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20of%20scientific%20methods%20were%20always%20present.%20Chirang%20was%20a%20backward%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%20early%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20learnt%20a%20great%20deal%20about%20agriculture%20while%20working%20on%20that%20leased%20land.%20After%20years%20of%20working%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20in%201995.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20learn%20more%2C%20an%20impromptu%20visit%20to%20the%20agriculture%20department%2C%20in%201998%2C%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20began%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20department%2C%20learning%20about%20agriculture%2C%20improving%20yields%2C%20finding%20ways%20to%20increase%20his%20profits%20each%20season%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20intercropping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVenturing%20into%20integrated%20farming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20areca%20nut%20crop%20takes%20years%20to%20start%20yielding.%20Even%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20yields%20are%20often%20not%20as%20high.%20%