.43-PM-1733988743-300x258.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-12-at-12.36.43-PM-1733988743-768x660.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-12-at-12.36.43-PM-1733988743-150x129.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-12-at-12.36.43-PM-1733988743.jpeg%201061w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388994%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERimjhim%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20stray%20dogs%20is%20what%20drives%20her%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20person%20who%20accidentally%20hit%20the%20dog%20did%20not%20do%20so%20on%20purpose.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20help%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20too.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20see%20the%20dog%20during%20the%20night%20and%20he%20was%20guiltridden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20this%20experience%2C%20Rimjhim%20found%20a%20way%20to%20address%20this%20issue.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20make%20roads%20safer%20for%20animals%20and%20people%20alike%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20into%20Pawsitivity%20%E2%80%94%20a%20successful%20venture%20focused%20on%20manufacturing%20QR-enabled%20reflective%20collars%20for%20stray%20animals%2C%20all%20made%20by%20a%20team%20of%20underprivileged%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20solution%20with%20a%20big%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20started%20making%20the%20collars%20in%20